text: <@UBS7QANF3> Hi Mo, thanks for adding more dates to the potential meetup; Im going to be at the other end UK in Edinburgh on business when the majority of you guys can make it, so Ill probably come to one of the future meetups. Just as an aside; if anyone is based in and around manchester I thought I may go to a local Python meetup that is being held 20th Jan In Manchester. Its not specific to Betfairlightweight, but Python in general. If so drop me a message. Its always good to meet like minded people. thanks (PS Happy New Year All !) :grinning:
